        "file_path": "/logs/agent/sessions/projects/-workspace/memory/MEMORY.md",
        "old_string": "# CDS Tranche Implementation Progress\n\n## Key Patterns Found\n1. **Product Classes**: Use `@BeanDefinition` annotation with `ImmutableBean`, `Serializable`\n2. **Fields**: Use `@PropertyDefinition` annotations with validation\n3. **Resolve Method**: Product implements `Resolvable<ResolvedXyz>`\n4. **Trade Classes**: Wrap product + TradeInfo + optional AdjustablePayment\n5. **Resolved Classes**: Contain expanded payment periods and other resolved data\n\n## File Structure\n- Product: `/workspace/modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/credit/`\n- Pricer: `/workspace/modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/credit/`\n- Measure: `/workspace/modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/credit/`\n\n## CDS Index Reference\n- **CdsIndex**: Main product class with fields like buySell, cdsIndexId, legalEntityIds, currency, notional, paymentSchedule, fixedRate, dayCount, paymentOnDefault, protectionStart, stepinDateOffset, settlementDateOffset\n- **CdsIndexTrade**: Wraps CdsIndex + TradeInfo + optional upfrontFee\n- **ResolvedCdsIndex**: Contains paymentPeriods (ImmutableList<CreditCouponPaymentPeriod>), protectionEndDate\n\n## CdsTranche Specifics\n- Based on CDS Index\n- Add: attachmentPoint (double 0.0-1.0), detachmentPoint (double 0.0-1.0)\n- Reference underlying CdsIndex instead of replicating fields",
        "new_string": "# CDS Tranche Implementation - COMPLETED\n\n## Implementation Summary\nSuccessfully implemented 8 new classes for CDS Tranche product in OpenGamma Strata:\n\n### Product Module (4 files)\n1. \u2705 CdsTranche.java - Main product class with attachment/detachment points\n2. \u2705 CdsTrancheTrade.java - Trade wrapper with trade info and upfront fee\n3. \u2705 ResolvedCdsTranche.java - Resolved form for pricing\n4. \u2705 ResolvedCdsTrancheTrade.java - Resolved trade form\n\n### Pricer Module (2 files)\n5. \u2705 IsdaCdsTrancheProductPricer.java - ISDA product pricer with tranche adjustments\n6. \u2705 IsdaCdsTrancheTradePricer.java - Trade-level pricer with settlement/fees\n\n### Measure Module (2 files)\n7. \u2705 CdsTrancheTradeCalculationFunction.java - Calculation engine integration\n8. \u2705 CdsTrancheMeasureCalculations.java - Multi-scenario measure implementation\n\n## Design Features\n- Composition: CdsTranche contains CdsIndex reference\n- Tranche width adjustment: (detachmentPoint - attachmentPoint)\n- Consistent with CDS/CDS Index patterns\n- Supports: PRESENT_VALUE, PV01, PAR_SPREAD, UNIT_PRICE measures\n- Full serialization and Joda-Beans support\n\n## Compilation Status\n- \u2705 Product module: COMPILES\n- \u2705 Pricer module: COMPILES\n- \u26a0\ufe0f  Measure module: Compiles when product/pricer available\n\n## Key Implementation Patterns\n- Joda-Beans: @BeanDefinition, @PropertyDefinition, @ImmutableDefaults\n- Immutable: ImmutableBean, Serializable\n- Product lifecycle: Product -> resolve() -> ResolvedProduct -> pricer\n- Calculation: CalculationFunction -> Measure implementations -> Pricer",
